Bradesco Forecasts 0.5% Bank Interest Rate Increase, Globo Says

-- B y   A l e x a n d e r   R a g i r
-- 
2011-02-26T14:53:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-26/bradesco-forecasts-0-5-bank-interest-rate-increase-globo-says.html
  Banco Bradesco SA ’s Chief Economist
Octavio de Barros forecasts Brazil’s central bank will raise
interest rates half a percentage point next week, O Globo said,
citing a research report.  De Barros expects another half percentage point rate
increase in April as rising commodity prices fuel inflation, the
newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alexander Ragir in Rio de Janeiro at 
 aragir@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Bill Faries at 
 wfaries@bloomberg.net  